WEBVTT

00:02:28.703 --> 00:02:32.647
to create a world
where women and girls are safe

00:02:32.671 --> 00:02:35.147
in their homes and at work,

00:02:35.171 --> 00:02:37.855
where all voices are represented

00:02:37.879 --> 00:02:39.580
and respected,

00:02:39.604 --> 00:02:42.362
all votes counted,

00:02:42.386 --> 00:02:44.490
the planet protected.

00:02:45.363 --> 00:02:47.273
And this is all possible.

00:02:47.969 --> 00:02:50.032
Because we're ready for this.

00:02:50.525 --> 00:02:54.787
We're better prepared
than any generation ever before us,

00:02:54.811 --> 00:02:56.908
better resourced, better connected.

00:02:56.932 --> 00:03:00.351
In many parts of the world,
we're living longer than ever.